{"tid":2084673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"衛星照片：伊朗地下導彈生產基地發生爆炸","createTime":"2020-06-29T11:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T06:53:18.000Z","uid":108359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"59758b69ff5c6558e6538865e93b0aca4ad60cc8","tid":2084673,"uid":108359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:32:31.000Z","msg":"歐洲衛星照片顯示，伊朗首都發生的爆炸與隱藏在東部山區的地下導彈生產基地有關。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗首都德黑蘭東部26日發生劇烈爆炸後，專業人士對歐盟委員會&ldquo;哨兵2號&rdquo;（Sentinel-2）27日拍攝的照片進行了分析。他們對美聯社指出，爆炸發生在德黑蘭東部山區，那裡隱藏著地下隧道和一個秘密導彈生產基地。衛星照片顯示，當地方圓數百米的灌木叢已成為一片焦土，而這在幾個星期前是不存在的。<br />\n<br />\n分析人士無法斷定究竟是什麼發生了爆炸，導致德黑蘭上空出現巨大的火球，也無法斷定爆炸的原因。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗國營電視台播放的畫面顯示，爆炸現場一棟建築物前置放的瓦斯氣瓶已經燒黑。伊朗國防部發言人說，那裡是一個&ldquo;公共地帶&rdquo;，是一個漏氣的瓦斯氣瓶引發了爆炸，無人在爆炸中死亡。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社指出，雖然是&ldquo;公共地帶&rdquo;，可在現場救援的都是軍人，不是當地的消防人員。伊朗國營電視台沒有回答這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n美國加州明德大學蒙特雷國際研究學院（Middlebury Institute of International Studies in Monterey）不擴散研究中心研究員欣茨（Fabian Hinz）對美聯社說，這個氣體存放地點在德黑蘭霍吉爾（Khojir）導彈基地附近，爆炸似乎炸毀了伊朗沙希德巴克雷工業集團（Shahid Bakeri Industrial Group）的一棟設施，那裡是製造固體助推火箭的地方。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社指出，華盛頓戰略與國際研究中心之前表示，霍吉爾（Khojir）&ldquo;有很多的隧道，部分被懷疑用來製造武器&rdquo;，當地大規模的工業建築物也顯示，那裡是導彈製造場所。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防情報局2019年指出，伊朗有中東地區最大規模的地下設施，&ldquo;用來支持德黑蘭彈道導彈能力的大部分領域，包括作戰部隊、導彈研發和生產計劃&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/iran-blast-struck-by-missile-site-06272020/5480548.html?fbclid=IwAR3N89IYvVVGpKorsQ82mzAQuhjvLIdeaGoQoZD_pWB8gCMWiHKd0uN7qZE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Firan-blast-struck-by-missile-site-06272020%2F5480548.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3N89IYvVVGpKorsQ82mzAQuhjvLIdeaGoQoZD_pWB8gCMWiHKd0uN7qZE&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=a4711ebc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/iran-blast-struck-by-missile-site-06272020/5480548.html?fbclid=IwAR3N89IYvVVGpKorsQ82mzAQuhjvLIdeaGoQoZD_pWB8gCMWiHKd0uN7qZE</a>"},{"pid":"86937d268eefad5ecba15453224c5fa32b6943f0","tid":2084673,"uid":264965,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"CIA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb870a6281454653a5c258510a1da25c636f9b83","tid":2084673,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86937d268eefad5ecba15453224c5fa32b6943f0","tid":2084673,"uid":264965,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"CIA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"Mossad啦"},{"pid":"29326271d519200112cbf7d1673018208a318e90","tid":2084673,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"試爆姐，準備攻打美國"},{"pid":"5bbe2b9090ab1c98604be8fec0d9e57c26431d7b","tid":2084673,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb870a6281454653a5c258510a1da25c636f9b83","tid":2084673,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86937d268eefad5ecba15453224c5fa32b6943f0","tid":2084673,"uid":264965,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"CIA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"Mossad啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"NO matter CIA or Mossad<br />\nEvil Axis boom boom boom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f59cc9b3e7dc4945cc5f8607a11d9248c22fb5","tid":2084673,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"伊朗又拎石頭砸自己的腳"},{"pid":"0e73edcd40d72f0789651e0b948277b274175467","tid":2084673,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"伊朗今年